> and I wonder: since the actual auth information appears to be missing (signified by {}?) A) where is the auth information actually stored on my macOS Docker Desktop and B) how do I carry it over into the Skopeo container?

Nice catch!  One way to approach it is doing a `skopeo login --authfile ...` on your desktop and inject that file into the container.

